{"tid":1734461,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點解我唔出去？","createTime":"2019-11-18T10:37:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T14:25:37.000Z","uid":127532,"like":36,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"999b1b9bf18783ee67b558ababc40d4d3035c2db","tid":1734461,"uid":127532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:37:48.000Z","msg":"點解我唔出去？<br />\n成個FB, IG都吹哂雞<br />\n但你唔想去，點解？無人陪，無裝備，驚俾人打，驚俾人拉<br />\n你唔敢出聲，扮無上網，怕俾人知你留左係屋企<br />\n<br />\n多年之後，大家都會講返今日<br />\n無論結果係點，今日將會係香港歷史重要既一日<br />\n今日係和理非話俾世界知，佢地唔係廢既一日<br />\n<br />\n多年之後，你會後悔，你會問自己<br />\n點解今日我無出去？<br />\n所有人都去到未來了，而你仲停留左響今日<br />\n<br />\n出去啦"},{"pid":"51b16469b7fd43d8fdc7be2c78fa4f2f60452385","tid":1734461,"uid":127532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:38:25.000Z","msg":"出去啦"},{"pid":"5c4dcfc762cc131b5627431c5955f9b9968fb486","tid":1734461,"uid":127532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:38:47.000Z","msg":"出去啦"},{"pid":"569c21d23e92f687f98c2b3d8ecd7091b6c4d407","tid":1734461,"uid":127532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:40:23.000Z","msg":"唔好俾將來既自己後悔"},{"pid":"0b43477bbfe9934559af4d490be617e47efb61a0","tid":1734461,"uid":6237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:41:10.000Z","msg":"水鏡先生, 唔多人會諗到咁遠<br />\n試下用再切身啲既理由<br />\n加油"},{"pid":"f7de0950ed2006a0cdfa7bee4164443e21e275bc","tid":1734461,"uid":127532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:47:42.000Z","msg":"唔好扮睇唔到"},{"pid":"280385b0be42843e2ad21a4a2be3cdcb85c2047d","tid":1734461,"uid":127395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:48:41.000Z","msg":"有一半軍師肯出嚟戰力已經好大分別<br />\n<br />\n連登冷氣軍師/返左工上連登既人入一入嚟<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/exPafS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/exPafS</a>"},{"pid":"75bb54e302e78d6967caa1d4833b00fe63f6b2a1","tid":1734461,"uid":2526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB